rows.label: tlk43300046_03_msg0001
rows.name:
...Well, whaddya know. The
head cook wasn't all talk...

rows.label: tlk43300046_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I challenged 'em to a contest of
dish-washing and veggie-peeling,
but they totally trounced me.

rows.label: tlk43300046_03_msg0003
rows.name:
So then I challenged 'em
to an axe contest...

rows.label: tlk43300046_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Our head cook isn't just a master
chef, but also a master combatant...

rows.label: tlk43300046_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Seems like it'll be a good long while
before the beautiful Queen Lagert
eats food that I've prepared...
